Hitachi, Mitsubishi Electric to Merge Their Hydropower Operations

-- B y   G o   O n o m i t s u
-- 
2011-08-04T06:45:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-04/hitachi-mitsubishi-electric-to-merge-hydropower-operations.html
Hitachi Ltd. (6501) ,  Mitsubishi Electric
Corp. (6503)  and  Mitsubishi Heavy Industries Ltd. (7011)  agreed to merge their
hydropower businesses.  The operations will be merged under a Hitachi hydropower
unit effective Oct 1., according to a statement to the Tokyo
Stock Exchange today. The companies had previously announced the
plan on March 30.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Go Onomitsu in Tokyo at 
 gonomitsu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gearoid Reidy at 
 greidy1@bloomberg.net  